cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper deals with the optimization of wireless networks using machine learning algorithms and focuses on the deployment of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs) for caching content. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also uses machine learning algorithms, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.IT (Information Theory). The optimization problem formulation and solution methodology suggest that it could also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
